entries.cant_work: Yousa be talkin' to mesa back here when yousa not bein' so busy, hey?
entries.next: Heydo! My busy workin' on de necklace for Raxa. My be stickin' on de termal detanator soon!
entries.notit_1: My tinkin' dat's not de ting my askin' you for.
entries.notit_2: Yousa bringin' mesa dat termal detanator? Disa not it.
entries.notyet: Sorry, mesa no can talk to you now.
entries.npc_1_1: Heydo! My workin' on makin' a necklace from Empire officer rank cylinder tings. My knowin' 'bout a warrant officer in de wilds wit some soldiers. My wantin' you to be killin' de warrant officer an' bringin' mesa hisa rank cylinder ting. Hey?
entries.npc_1_2: Ello! My workin' hard on de necklace for Raxa Binn. My needin' a nice pendant now -- mesa tinkin' a termal detanator. Yousa mebbe killin' disa Empire Army captain an' gettin' it for mesa?
entries.npc_2_1: Oie boie, yousa good friend. My givin' yousa de coordinates right now. Yousa bringin' de cylinder ting back to me, hey?
entries.npc_2_2: Owoo! My givin' yousa de coordinates right now. Disa captain, hesa got mooie bombad troopers wit him, so yousa be careful, hey?
entries.npc_4_1: Here at Zephyr Base wesa plannin' strategies for fightin' de Empire on Naboo. My bein' liyayzonn to all Gungans on Naboo, gettin' dere hep.
entries.npc_4_2: Ooh, one time mesa overhearin' Raxa Binn, shesa sayin, "Evvy tim I seein' dat Gungan, I want a termal detanator."
entries.npc_5_1: My be sweetin' on de commando trainer here, Raxa Binn. Shesa mooie-mooie! My tinkin' shesa likin' a necklace made of Empire rank cylinder tings.
entries.npc_5_2: Disa one of Colonel Zarvold's men. Raxa Binn, shesa hatin' Zarvold -- mesa not knowin' why -- an' will like dis detanator for, mesa thinkin', sentimental value.
entries.npc_6_1: Ooah, de rank cylinder tings for warrant officers bein' just de right color for matchin' Raxa Binn's eyes!
entries.npc_6_2: Hesa Cap'n Rohd Gostervek, mooie bombad Imperial. Hesa patrollin' de wilderness, lookin' for dis base. Hesa always protected, so yousa be careful, hey?
entries.npc_backtowork_1: My not knowin' anyting else to be tellin' yousa, sorry.
entries.npc_backtowork_2: My not knowin' anyting else to be tellin' yousa, sorry.
entries.npc_breech_1: It's a Rebel! Protect me, you fools!
entries.npc_failure_1: Yousa no got de rank cylinder ting? Awoo, my never gonna finish disa necklace for Raxa.
entries.npc_failure_2: Owoo! No termal detanator? Mooie bombad! Raxa Binn, shesa nevah likin' mesa now!
entries.npc_noloc_1: My waitin' now for coordinates for de Empire patrol. Yousa be checkin' wit mesa soon, hey?
entries.npc_noloc_2: My waitin' for Zephyr Base tellin' where's disa captain. Yousa talkin' to mesa real soon, hey?
entries.npc_reset_1: Dat okay wit mesa. Yousa go be doin' your works, hey?
entries.npc_reward_1: Oie boie! Disa de just-right ting mesa needin' on de necklace for Raxa! Tanks! Yousa be talkin' to mesa 'gain soon, hey?
entries.npc_reward_2: Ooh, yousa bombad! Disa gonna be de sweetest necklace for de sweetest Zabrak commando trainer in de worl'. Shesa seein' dis an' gettin' all soft an' sweet ovah mesa. Tanks!
entries.npc_work_1: Yousa gettin' dat rank cylinder ting yet? My workin' on Raxa's necklace berry hard.
entries.npc_work_2: Yousa not gettin' dat termal detanator yet? My workin' berry hard on de necklace.
entries.player_3_2: Why do you want a thermal detonator for a necklace pendant?
entries.player_4_1: Who is getting the gift necklace you're making?
entries.player_4_2: Why do you want a detonator from this particular Imperial Army captain?
entries.player_5_1: Why does the rank cylinder have to be from this warrant officer?
entries.player_5_2: Who is the Imperial Army captain?
entries.player_reset_1: I don't want this mission right now.
entries.player_sorry_1: I'll keep working on the mission.
entries.return_waypoint_description_1: Gungan liaison to the Zephyr Base Alliance outpost on Rori, currently waiting for an Imperial rank cylinder that he wants to add to a necklace.
entries.return_waypoint_description_2: Gungan liaison to the Zephyr Base Alliance outpost on Rori, currently waiting for a thermal detonator to use as a necklace pendant.
entries.waypoint_description_1: On patrol from Colonel Zarvold's Imperial Army battalion on Rori, this officer carries an Imperial rank cylinder sought by Booto Lubble, Gungan liaison to the Zephyr Base Alliance outpost on Rori.
entries.waypoint_description_2: A patrol from Colonel Zarvold's Imperial Army battalion on Rori, equipped with a thermal detonator sought by Booto Lubble, Gungan liaison to the Zephyr Base Alliance outpost.
entries.npc_reset_2: Dat okay wit mesa.  Yousa go be doin' your works, hey?
entries.player_reset_2: I don't want this mission right now.
